data.text: @theMihirV Govt should start the booster dose so by the time of June a good amount of people can be vaccinated and have lesser impact
@theMihirV Countries which received Pfizer and Moderna vaccines had the highest morbidity and mortality.

@theMihirV Not strange atall.  Its to be expected.  Countries with best management of lockdowns & covid protocols had the lowest natural immunity, consequently highest Omicron.  vaccine efficacy is much touted, but equally in doubted; maybe it lowers hospitalizations (maybe).
